# TPT2 Module Blueprints (Current Account State)

Single source of truth for import-ready module blobs.

## Import Notes
- A trailing `=` (or `==`) at the end of a blob is normal base64 padding.
- Do not remove that padding.
- If import fails, recopy the full blob with no spaces/newlines.

## Current Missing Modules

- `attack.shatter` (Shatter)
- `shield.universal` (Universal Shield)
